text: William McEvoy (1845 - 14 July 1930) was an Australian cricketer. He played one first-class cricket match for Victoria in 1877. ==See also== * List of Victoria first-class cricketers ==References== ==External links== * Category:1845 births Category:1930 deaths Category:Australian cricketers Category:Victoria cricketers Category:Cricketers from Sydney Category:Melbourne Cricket Club cricketers
